Title=WOTC_DisplayHitChance
Description=[h1][b]WOTC - Extended Information![/b][/h1]

[b]After a lot of work, we are happy to bring you a WOTC enhanced and rewritten version of Perfect Information![/b]

So, the aim of this mod is to provide you with the maximum details and information about what's happening on the battlefield.

[h1][b]FEATURES[/b][/h1]

[b]General[/b]
[list]
[*]Aim Assist display everywhere
[*]Show Miss Chance instead of Hit Chance everywhere
[/list]
[b]Flyovers[/b]
[list]
[*]Display Hit/Crit/Dodge Chances in Damages Flyovers during Battle (works with all types of direct damages)
[*]HitChance is now displayed in Flyovers for non-damaging Abilities like Mind Control, Mind Spin and Mind Scorch!
[/list]
[b]ShotBar[/b]
[list]
[*]Display Grimy Shotbar
[/list]
[b]ShotHUD[/b]
[list]
[*]Display Graze Chances and Crit Damage
[*]Preview Minimum Damage in TacticalUI when aiming at an enemy
[*]Preview Hacking in TacticalShotHUD when aiming at Haywire-able Enemy, or Hackable Objective/Item*Configurable by MCM
[/list]
[b]ShotWings[/b]
[list]
[*]Crit Damages Details in Right Wing and Damages Bonus Details in Left Wing
[/list]
[b]Tooltips[/b]
[list]
[*]Reworked Soldier Info Stats List Tooltip shows when hovering mouse over Soldier Name
[*]Reworked Soldier Buffs / Debuffs Tooltip shows when hovering mouse over Soldier Buff/Debuff
[*]New Enemy Stats / Abilities / Buffs / Debuffs Tooltip shows when hovering mouse over enemy HUD Icon (little Heads over tactical HUD when enemy is in line of sight)
[*]Reworked Weapon Tooltip shows when hovering mouse over Weapon Icon
[*]Reworked Ability Tooltip shows when hovering mouse over Ability Icon
[/list]

[h1][b]LOCALIZATION[/b][/h1]

We also added localization integration, so you can translate the little damage Strings into your language.
Feel free to do so.
You can find those files under <Steam install>\SteamApps\workshop\content\268500\1183444470\Localization.

